{"tid":571722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"景泰苑減音窗不減音 居民失眠頭痛 長開冷氣自救","createTime":"2018-02-25T02:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T05:32:51.000Z","uid":10540,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca4319c4aa6248d930189dfff67c9c9a3c4828c","tid":571722,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180224/large/1519477597_01d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F1519477597_01d1.jpg&h=31285cd8&s={SIZE}\" />減音窗將不可能建屋的土地變成可能，但有新蒲崗景泰苑住戶嫌減音窗減音效果不彰，索性拆除減音窗，關閉窗戶開冷氣，亦有保留減音窗的住戶稱，即使有減音窗，晚上仍然非常嘈吵，令人頭痛，難以入睡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180224/large/1519477616_4267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F1519477616_4267.jpg&h=0fbf59e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新蒲崗景泰苑是第一個安裝減音窗的公營房屋項目，項目受太子道東噪音困擾，房署遂於大廈3至32樓6至23號單位（3至8樓的13、16號單位外）安裝減音窗，1樓及2樓亦有部分單位安裝，確保居民受到的噪音符合環保署噪音不多於75分貝的要求。房署於項目售樓說明書上列明，業主不得干擾、改動、變更或拆除裝設在單位內的減音窗或固定窗，除非是根據公契規定作保養、維修或更換，而明年入伙的觀塘彩興苑樓書亦有同樣要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180224/large/1519477612_d0f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F1519477612_d0f5.jpg&h=833a7860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170910/photo/bkn-20170910102637423-0910_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170910144505\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170910%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170910102637423-0910_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170910144505&h=9c5e5132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n減音窗的原理是把兩塊玻璃板平行排列並於對邊側各設開口，阻隔交通噪音，同時維持空氣自然流通。不過，不少景泰苑業主嫌減音窗不減音，不顧規定拆窗。居民吳女士稱入伙裝修時已拆除減音窗，「試過分別唔大」，稱開了窗就無法隔音，索性整塊拆除，現時就「閂哂窗，熱天就開冷氣」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">居民何太則直言，「覺得（減音窗）係廢架囉，冇用架」，又稱自己睡在窗邊，無法入眠，令她飽受頭痛之苦，又謂隔籬鄰舍均已拆去減音窗，既「齖齰」，抹窗又難。其就讀中學的兒子何先生則指，減音窗作用輕微，晚上如有電單車或大貨車便會很嘈吵，「好專注時畀佢嚇一嚇，或窒一窒」，又稱除非全屋窗戶全部關上，即使廚房開窗，亦會很嘈吵，「大窗（減音窗）都冇乜用」。</span><br />\n<br />\n房署表示，業主入伙時須簽署保證書，表示承諾遵守「景泰苑裝修指引」及「裝修須知」，如景泰苑管理處發現拆去或改動減音窗，會採取適當行動，而辦事處已張貼告示，提醒業主自行拆除減音窗會違反大廈公契條款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180225/57868077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57868077&d=XyEbFIQmaurJHCY37uFycIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bde102a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57868077&h=17459688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180225/57868077</a>"},{"pid":"a934b76bec6d9adce769b0c279b6e62fcc4a684a","tid":571722,"uid":71391,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"個窗做下樣啫<br />\n<br />\nd 住戶咁認真嘅"},{"pid":"c3b558446ca408e57c574a295a0da85f80da7da4","tid":571722,"uid":17980,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"退返俾政府囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aa8c929b29ead8582f098576182a1219cb2915","tid":571722,"uid":53122,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"d死窮鬼有得住仲嫌三嫌四"},{"pid":"9442e8b7826056d0e6ab25268fc98022a9ceb4d0","tid":571722,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"九龍城老街坊：成班廢柴"},{"pid":"b05f77f151a12fa144a376cb214c5ebf8876643b","tid":571722,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"如房署告居民違反大廈公契<br />\n留名等居民反告房署賣樓不符合環保署規定"},{"pid":"09e7ffd4e7e3e0e6f4348885d0ed5db58ffa197c","tid":571722,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:59:53.000Z","msg":"訓洒店"},{"pid":"90a6ed99090774fc6944dbbfc9f0c2b82b757f6c","tid":571722,"uid":113074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"隔音窗都得condom都得啦"},{"pid":"251f8d7bc135309b7f01dfbf83c76d62620b8ecc","tid":571722,"uid":117477,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"住得入去就預咗咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc900442a9802991b8f0829f0e0133c2b280679","tid":571722,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62aa8c929b29ead8582f098576182a1219cb2915","tid":571722,"uid":53122,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"d死窮鬼有得住仲嫌三嫌四"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"綠置居都窮鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b62511c54aa9641ac37bd22a7502c8e4bbebcd","tid":571722,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"上面好幾個留言顯示支那臭蟲論歷久不衰"},{"pid":"9e825a6312c90650162667d8bf7934baafc0be0d","tid":571722,"uid":445,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"以前飛機飛過咪又係咁瞓"},{"pid":"2a7e5825a13e4e425f2408bc0013dd1ef8e7eb15","tid":571722,"uid":37240,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"隔音窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑撚死咩 咁都得<br />\nD band房就唔洗用幾十萬整隔音層啦"},{"pid":"6eb37c4e44132cb5955016237777c9f4cd681be7","tid":571722,"uid":58791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"塊玻璃好薄根本唔開窗都隔唔到音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知房署點設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個趟窗又係癈既，10戶有8戶都拆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi