2F20180224%2Flarge%2F1519477612_d0f5.jpg&h=833a7860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170910/photo/bkn-20170910102637423-0910_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170910144505\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170910%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170910102637423-0910_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170910144505&h=9c5e5132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n減音窗的原理是把兩塊玻璃板平行排列並於對邊側各設開口，阻隔交通噪音，同時維持空氣自然流通。不過，不少景泰苑業主嫌減音窗不減音，不顧規定拆窗。居民吳女士稱入伙裝修時已拆除減音窗，「試過分別唔大」，稱開了窗就無法隔音，索性整塊拆除，現時就「閂哂窗，熱天就開冷氣」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">居民何太則直言，「覺得（減音窗）係廢架囉，冇用架」，又稱自己睡在窗邊，無法入眠，令她飽受頭痛之苦，又謂隔籬鄰舍均已拆去減音窗，既「齖齰」，抹窗又難。其就讀中學的兒子何先生則指，減音窗作用輕微，晚上如有電單車或大貨車便會很嘈吵，「好專注時畀佢嚇一嚇，或窒一窒」，又稱除非全屋窗戶全部關上，即使廚房開窗，亦會很嘈吵，「大窗（減音窗）都冇乜用」。</span><br />\n<br />\n房署表示，業主入伙時須簽署保證書，表示承諾遵守「景泰苑裝修指引」及「裝修須知」，如景泰苑管理處發現拆去或改動減音窗，會採取適當行動，而辦事處已張貼告示，提醒業主自行拆除減音窗會違反大廈公契條款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180225/57868077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57868077&d=XyEbFIQmaurJHCY37uFycIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bde102a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57868077&h=17459688\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180225/57868077</a></blockquote><br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"5ae4bee767468efaf0de931b3fe0568ff5e4f123","tid":571722,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d死窮鬼有得住仲嫌三嫌四</blockquote>綠置居都窮鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你明知嗰度有馬路嘈先貪平都買"},{"pid":"910a86b63ef197f829be0bbb6927f318ed6d5ee9","tid":571722,"uid":19842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"段片好撚多支那口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b34640eba1a31b2d50b1e85c97ed912dd0c5afe","tid":571722,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"咁慘唔好住快啲搬走啦"},{"pid":"3668383fd6757c13c21a84d1757c0c2307dbb73f","tid":571722,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"咪又係蝗民住<br />\nwfc"},{"pid":"7afa5776cb80cb45f67a09bda8c2aa92539d90bc","tid":571722,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"住戶唔識新科技啫"},{"pid":"4c70cb4abb3efb6e23d8ceb7d84b557105a1cb6e","tid":571722,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"戴耳塞訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed726f1b6572eafdab32a042cf32ed842a2b063","tid":571722,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05f77f151a12fa144a376cb214c5ebf8876643b","tid":571722,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"如房署告居民違反大廈公契<br />\n留名等居民反告房署賣樓不符合環保署規定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"當銀望盤拍賣啦<br />\n咁多人上唔到車"}]}